Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.50,0:25:06.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,430)\fad(350,0)\3c&H24B328&}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.25,0:25:06.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,715)\fad(350,0)\3c&H24B328&}薄荷冰淇淋
